@startuml DFD_Level0_Context_Diagram

skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title DFD Level 0: PawPal System Context Diagram

' External Entities
actor "Pet Owner" as Owner <<External Entity>>
actor "Veterinarian" as Vet <<External Entity>>
actor "Caregiver" as Caregiver <<External Entity>>
actor "Seller" as Seller <<External Entity>>
actor "System Administrator" as Admin <<External Entity>>
database "OpenStreetMap API" as OSM <<External System>>
database "Groq LLM API" as Groq <<External System>>
database "Firebase Cloud Messaging" as FCM <<External System>>
database "Blockchain Network\n(BTC/ETH/USDT)" as Blockchain <<External System>>

' Main System
rectangle "PawPal\nPet Care Management System" as PawPal <<Process 0>>

' Pet Owner flows
Owner --> PawPal : Credentials / Pet Info /\nHealth Queries / Pet Photos /\nMarketplace Orders /\nCommunity Posts /\nLost-Found Alerts /\nBooking Requests /\nPayment
PawPal --> Owner : Auth Token / Breed Predictions /\nAI Health Guidance /\nOrder Confirmations /\nCommunity Feed /\nCaregiver Location /\nAppointment Confirmations /\nNotifications

' Veterinarian flows
Vet --> PawPal : Clinic Info / Availability /\nAppointment Status
PawPal --> Vet : Appointment Requests /\nPet Medical History /\nNotifications

' Caregiver flows
Caregiver --> PawPal : Profile & Services /\nAvailability / GPS Location /\nService Updates /\nCompletion Reports
PawPal --> Caregiver : Booking Requests /\nService Schedule /\nNotifications

' Seller flows
Seller --> PawPal : Product Listings /\nOrder Status Updates /\nInventory Updates
PawPal --> Seller : Order Notifications /\nSales Analytics /\nPayment Credits

' Admin flows
Admin --> PawPal : Moderation Actions /\nUser Management /\nContent Removal
PawPal --> Admin : System Stats /\nAll Module Data /\nDashboard Analytics

' External API flows
PawPal --> OSM : GPS Coordinates /\nClinic Search Query
OSM --> PawPal : Nearby Clinics Data

PawPal --> Groq : Contextualized Query /\nPet Profile Context
Groq --> PawPal : AI-Generated Response

PawPal --> FCM : Notification Payload /\nUser Device Tokens
FCM --> PawPal : Delivery Status

PawPal --> Blockchain : Crypto Payment Request /\nWallet Address
Blockchain --> PawPal : Transaction Confirmation

note right of PawPal
  Context Level (Level 0)
  Shows the entire PawPal system
  as a single process with all
  external entities and data flows.

  System includes:
  - Flutter Mobile App (iOS/Android)
  - Next.js Admin Portal
  - Golang Modular Monolith Backend
  - Python FastAPI AI Services
  - PostgreSQL / Redis / ChromaDB
end note

@enduml
